#232 - make module factory return a module name

Allow doing something like this:

```
var angular = require('angular');
var app = angular.module('app', [
  require('angular-chart')
]);
```

Allow passing hex colours in `colours` attribute

    $scope.colors = ['#FD1F5E','#1EF9A1','#7FFD1F','#68F000'];

Fix #57, #42
